15:["$","h2",null,{"children":"3. How to Submit a Request"}]
16:["$","p",null,{"children":"To exercise any of your rights under the CCPA, you may submit a verifiable consumer request through the following methods:"}]
17:["$","ul",null,{"children":["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Email:"}]," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"mailto:support@revia.bio","className":"text-blue-600 hover:underline","children":"support@revia.bio"}]," ","with the subject line \"CCPA Request\""]}]}]
18:["$","p",null,{"children":"Your request must provide sufficient information to allow us to reasonably verify that you are the person about whom we collected personal information (or an authorized representative) and describe your request with enough detail to allow us to understand, evaluate, and respond to it. We cannot respond to your request or provide personal information if we cannot verify your identity or authority to make the request."}]
19:["$","h2",null,{"children":"4. Verification Process"}]
1a:["$","p",null,{"children":"Upon receiving your request, we will verify your identity by matching information you provide with information we already have on file. We may request additional information to confirm your identity. Only you, or an authorized agent registered with the California Secretary of State, may make a verifiable consumer request related to your personal information. You may make a verifiable consumer request on behalf of your minor child."}]
1b:["$","h2",null,{"children":"5. Do Not Sell My Personal Information"}]
1c:["$","p",null,{"children":["ReVia does not sell personal information in exchange for monetary consideration. To the extent any sharing of data with third parties may be considered a \"sale\" under the CCPA, you may opt out by contacting us at"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"mailto:support@revia.bio","className":"text-blue-600 hover:underline","children":"support@revia.bio"}]," ","with the subject line \"Do Not Sell My Personal Information.\" We will process your request within fifteen (15) business days."]}]
1d:["$","h2",null,{"children":"6. Response Timeframe"}]
1e:["$","p",null,{"children":"We will acknowledge receipt of your verifiable consumer request within ten (10) business days. We will respond to your request within forty-five (45) days of receipt. If we require additional time, we will inform you of the reason and the extension period in writing. Any extension will not exceed an additional forty-five (45) days. If we are unable to fulfill your request, we will explain the reasons in our response."}]
1f:["$","h2",null,{"children":"7. Authorized Agent"}]
20:["$","p",null,{"children":"You may designate an authorized agent to submit requests on your behalf. To do so, you must provide the authorized agent with written permission signed by you, and we may require you to verify your own identity directly with us. Alternatively, the authorized agent may provide a power of attorney pursuant to California Probate Code sections 4000 to 4465."}]
21:["$","h2",null,{"children":"8. Contact Us"}]
22:["$","p",null,{"children":"For questions about this CCPA Notice or to exercise your rights, please contact us at:"}]
